## Call for Participation

Join the Digital Accessibility Framework (DAF) monthly town halls starting on September 11th, 2025. These are intended to engage public participation in this promising project. Each town hall is scheduled for 10:00 am US Eastern (14:00 UTC) on the second Thursday of each month.  

In order to put together a comprehensive, top down look at disability needs â€“ we need your help!  

We are looking for:
- disability advocates, 
-researchers on accessibility and disability, and 
- technologists who care about accessibility 
to join us and explore the framework together so we can create the best tool possible. 

Please complete our [sign-up](https://forms.gle/gnPZYH8gKDui58jv9) form to receive an invitation to the meetings.